<subSubSection id="31DC896F9D1BD6548EDE1B615FD8B8C9" pageId="0" pageNumber="133" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="1363841E559B4509FC432CF56D31BD07" pageId="0" pageNumber="133">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2DD8D41A16AD07879FFFE6B8D0775030" pageId="0" pageNumber="133">The species epithet is named in honor of Ms. Jiang-Hai He, a local staff in Huanglian Shan National Nature Reserve, who has worked there for almost 30 years and made a big contribution to the knowledge of biodiversity of this nature reserve, and is also the discoverer of this new species.</paragraph>
